  <string name="settings_service_upstream_help">Regex ya kiolesura kikuu cha juu inayotumika kuelekeza upya trafiki ya chini. VPN Hotspot yenyewe lazima iruhusiwe kutumia VPN hiyo ili ifanye kazi. Tumia &lt;tt&gt;none&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;a^&lt;/tt&gt;, au regex nyingine batili kuzuia tethering kupitia VPN.</string>
  <string name="settings_upstream_fallback_help">Upstream mbadala hutumika VPN inapoacha baadhi ya njia kwenye mtandao chaguomsingi. Tumia &lt;tt&gt;none&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;a^&lt;/tt&gt;, au regex nyingine batili kukataza mbadala.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_masquerade_none_summary">Usiandike upya anwani chanzo au port za downstream. Hii inaweza kufanya kazi vizuri na VPN bandia kama vizuia matangazo au socksifier, lakini haipaswi kutumiwa na VPN halisi.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_masquerade_simple_summary">Andika upya anwani chanzo na port za downstream katika kanuni za routing zinazomilikiwa na programu.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_masquerade_netd_summary">Iombe Android &lt;tt&gt;netd&lt;/tt&gt; ishughulikie masquerade. Android inaweza kuongeza nyongeza za platform kama ushughulikiaji wa &lt;tt&gt;FTP&lt;/tt&gt; na vihesabu vya tethering, lakini hii haifai unapoficha shughuli za tethering kutoka kwa mtoa huduma.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_ipv6_mode_system_summary">Acha ushughulikiaji wa IPv6 kwa usanidi wa routing wa mfumo.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_ipv6_mode_block_summary">Zuia uvujaji wa IPv6 kwenye violesura vya downstream.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_ipv6_mode_nat_summary">Huweka ULA &lt;tt&gt;/64&lt;/tt&gt; ya programu iliyo deterministic na ku-proxy IPv6 ya downstream &lt;tt&gt;TCP&lt;/tt&gt;/&lt;tt&gt;UDP&lt;/tt&gt; pamoja na best-effort &lt;tt&gt;ICMPv6&lt;/tt&gt; kupitia root daemon. Hii ni kazi ya nafasi ya mtumiaji, si packet NAT kamili, na haisambazi IPv6 next-header protocols nyingine.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_auto_start">Anzisha huduma kiotomatiki</string>
  <string name="settings_service_auto_start_summary">Rejesha huduma ikiwa zilikuwa zinaendeshwa kabla ya kifaa kuwashwa upya au programu kusasishwa.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_repeater_supplicant_mode_warning">Majina mafupi ya mtandao yanaweza kuhitaji hali ya Supplicant</string>
  <string name="settings_service_temp_hotspot_use_system">Tumia usanidi wa mfumo kwa hotspot ya muda</string>
  <string name="settings_service_temp_hotspot_use_system_summary">Itagongana na programu nyingine zinazotumia hotspot ya ndani pekee. Pia hutumia rasilimali zaidi chinichini isipokuwa imesakinishwa kama programu ya mfumo.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_temp_hotspot_use_system_summary_api30">Itagongana na programu nyingine zinazotumia hotspot ya ndani pekee. Pia hutumia rasilimali zaidi chinichini isipokuwa imesakinishwa kama programu ya mfumo. Huenda ikafanya kazi kwenye Android 12 au mpya zaidi.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock">Weka Wi‑Fi hai</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_none">Chaguomsingi la mfumo</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_high_perf_v29">Zima kuokoa nishati</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_low_latency">Hali ya ucheleweshaji mdogo</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_none_summary">Tumia tabia chaguomsingi ya nishati ya Wi‑Fi ya mfumo ili kuokoa betri.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_high_perf_v29_summary">Hupunguza latency ya pakiti kwa hali kama simu za sauti baada ya skrini kuzimwa. Inahitaji usaidizi wa hardware. Kwenye Android 14 na mpya zaidi, hali hii iliyopitwa na wakati hubadilishwa na hali ya latency ya chini.</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_low_latency_summary">Huboresha matumizi yanayoathiriwa na latency kama michezo au uhalisia pepe. Inaweza kupunguza muda wa betri, throughput, marudio ya kuchanganua Wi‑Fi, ubora wa roaming na usahihi wa eneo. Inahitaji usaidizi wa hardware na programu hii iendeshwe mbele huku skrini ikiwa imewashwa.</string>
