  <string name="wifi_bridged_mode_opportunistic_shutdown_help">Katika bridged AP mode, Android inaweza kuzima AP instance isiyotumika baada ya bridged timeout: %s</string>
  <string name="wifi_hotspot_timeout_bridged">Muda wa kutotumika kwa instance ya daraja</string>
  <string name="wifi_hotspot_timeout_bridged_help">Sanidi muda ambao AP instance ya bridged iliyo idle inasubiri kabla ya opportunistic shutdown. Ikiwa instances zote mbili ni idle, Android huzima instance yenye frequency ya juu. overall hotspot timeout bado hutumika kando.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Default: %s</string>
